Here is another good idea for you.  If you can manage to find the camp empty (rare), try the Ancient Croc in Guk.  The crocs PHs are great exp, and they don't aggro.  The Ancient croc himself is level 30, a tough battle but do-able for you.  Plus, the Gatorscale sleeves and legs are very nice items to wear, and you can sell them for a BIG chunk of money.<P>Shiri
