<HR size="1" color="#dedfdf">
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Well, I have a Paladin that has a hard time soloing high greens at her level!<P>But, you are right, it really is a matter of doing a little research to find a good spot.  You want to find either single spawns or multi-spawns that don't aggro.  You possibly can solo yellows and reds, but it's simply not worth it.  It will take all of your mana, and your pet's HP, to do it, and increases the chances that you will die and lose all the exp you just gained.  A nice steady stream of high blues is what you want to find.<P>Shiri
</FONT>
