AT LAST, SOMEONE WHO UNDERSTANDS MAGES!<P>After a while, i started to look at a mage as less powerful. sure they can nuke pretty damn good and their pets do ample damage, but i dont think that they are an awesome, godly class as everybody mentions. my friend once mentioned that "mages are gods" at higher levels, and i simply dont see that, they seem to get less powerful the higher i go up (compared to other classes) one of my friends has a pally (supposedly the least damage dealing class or something) and hes soloing the same things as easy as i do in OT. i just pretty much think that we need a much larger variety of spells than we have - pretty much nuke, DS, pet. i still like being a mage and all, but i just think we need some new things.<P>Mimarin Kirigoe<BR>37th Mage<BR>Mithaniel Marr
